response.original_title: Kenny and Corky Singing Nuttin’ for Christmas
response.overview: This compilation of classic cartoons is headlined by a short film of puppets Kenny and Corky singing their 1959 hit cover of the holiday novelty song "Nuttin’ for Christmas". Also features Tex Avery's A Day at the Zoo and Ub Iwerks' Summertime,  among others.
response.title: Kenny and Corky Singing Nuttin’ for Christmas
